---
title: Cheese Tortellini Puttanesca with Roasted Parmesan-Crusted Cauliflower
description: Puttanesca hails from Naples, Italy and is one of its most famous exports. A base made from pantry staples like olives and Worcestershire imparts this dish with rich, savoury flavours that are hard to forget!
